			description: [
				"Here is the list of commands you have access to:"
				""
				"&2/hat &rallows you to put the item you are wearing on your head."
				""
				"&2/leaderboard &rlets you view stats."
				""
				"&2/rec &rlets you tell other players that you're recording or streaming."
				""
				"&2/trashcan &ropens a trash can so you can throw away any type of item."
				""
				"&2/sethome &rand &2/home &rlet you set your personal spawn point."
				""
				"&2/spawn &rlets you teleport to your world's spawn point."
				"&5(If you're an admin, remember to redefine your world spawn point with the /setworldspawn command.)"
				""
				"&2/tpa [USERNAME] &rlets you send a teleportation request to another player."
			]
