				""
				"&3/skyblock team <new name>"
				"Rename your team, created at the same time as your island."
				""
				"&3/skyblock home"
				"Teleport you back to your spawn Island (not the server Spawn)"
				""
				"&3/skyblock join <team>"
				"Join a team."
				""
				"&3/skyblock leave"
				"Leave you team (so your Island)"
				""
